rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Hiyokkoo not want to salvage any more!
Always feeling like useless beginner,
and it no fun at all!

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Really? Don't you like it when
you find something good and it
makes you money?

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0003
rows.name:
And doesn't it make you feel curious
when you find mysterious treasures
that nobody's seen before?

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I mean, sure, we have to deal with
scary monsters sometimes, but I feel
like the excitement makes up for it.

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Hiyokkoo think is more scary than excite.
Rex know about average mortality of
salvagers per year?

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0006
rows.name:
No... What is it?
About 20 or so?

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0007
rows.name:
Is 360 people! Every year!
Almost same number as Nopon who
die from eat poison mushroom!

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0008
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Maybe you should do something
about those poison mushrooms first...

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0009
rows.name:
Ohhhh, Hiyokkoo want out of
dangerous career!
